---
// Services section with business areas
---

<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-gray-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl floating parallax"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 w-80 h-80 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl floating parallax"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full text-secondary font-medium text-sm mb-4" data-aos="fade-up">
        事業一覧
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        私たちの<span class="gradient-text">主要事業</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        FRONTOLIAインターネットは、IT関連の多様な事業を展開し、ユーザーのインターネット体験を向上させるサービスを提供しています。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Service 1: Cloud Servers -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden card-hover" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary/5 rounded-bl-full"></div>
        
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">MINEPLAYERBOX</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          安価かつユーザー密着型のゲームサーバーレンタルをしています。
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">聞きやすいサポート体制</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">柔軟なスケーリング</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">あなた好みのカスタマイズ</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-secondary font-medium animated-underline">
          詳細を見る
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Service 2: E-Sports -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden card-hover" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/5 rounded-bl-full"></div>
        
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">EverBloom</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          あなたの大切な瞬間を美しい動画に。動画編集サービス
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">思い通りに最高の動画を編集</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">卒業、結婚動画などすべてに対応</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-accent mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-600">編集者と直接相談で低価格を実現</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://everbloom.frontolia.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center text-secondary font-medium animated-underline">
          詳細を見る
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>